## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on publicly available opinions and articles, which may not encompass the full spectrum of perspectives on gun ownership. Additionally, the arguments presented are often influenced by cultural, political, and personal biases, which can affect the objectivity of the sources. The report does not include empirical data or statistical analysis, which would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of the impact of gun ownership on society.

